Moriguchi-sensei's one-man operation.

274
00:15:22,554 --> 00:15:23,722
We have to stop him.

275
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:25,257
I know.

276
00:15:26,058 --> 00:15:27,726
But if we take our time,

277
00:15:27,793 --> 00:15:30,930
Naito and the others will end up expelled.

278
00:15:33,365 --> 00:15:34,500
Right.

279
00:15:35,067 --> 00:15:36,535
Why don't you come with me?

280
00:15:36,602 --> 00:15:39,204
It might help you relieve some stress.

281
00:15:39,271 --> 00:15:41,173
Mom, we haven't finished talking…

282
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,107
Oh…

283
00:15:42,942 --> 00:15:44,143
sorry.

284
00:15:44,209 --> 00:15:46,045
I'm really sorry.

285
00:15:46,111 --> 00:15:47,479
Maybe you should go.

286
00:15:47,546 --> 00:15:48,814
Yes.

287
00:15:56,322 --> 00:15:58,490
KOBAYAKAWA

288
00:16:00,626 --> 00:16:02,127
What's wrong? It's late.

289
00:16:05,464 --> 00:16:07,366
Hina-chan, it's been a while.

290
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,068
Excuse me!

291
00:16:10,102 --> 00:16:13,272
I came to ask you a favor!

292
00:16:13,339 --> 00:16:14,740
A favor? From me?

293
00:16:14,807 --> 00:16:18,510
Could you please ask the school
to cancel Iroha's expulsion?

294
00:16:19,078 --> 00:16:20,346
Please!

295
00:16:23,282 --> 00:16:26,151
