296
00:16:30,022 --> 00:16:31,190
All right.

297
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:33,225
It's okay.

298
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:38,130
You want Naito's expulsion
to be cancelled?

299
00:16:38,197 --> 00:16:41,000
My daughter asked me to.

300
00:16:41,066 --> 00:16:42,001
Are you going to say no?

301
00:16:44,169 --> 00:16:46,805
If we overturn a decision,
it'll undermine our authority--

302
00:16:46,872 --> 00:16:51,143
I've done… a lot for Meishin.

303
00:16:52,411 --> 00:16:53,245
You'll do it, right?

304
00:16:59,351 --> 00:17:02,855
Can you… let me handle things for now?

305
00:17:06,592 --> 00:17:07,626
Starting today,

306
00:17:08,193 --> 00:17:10,429
five second-year students
will serve a house suspension.

307
00:17:11,130 --> 00:17:13,265
The six students
recommended for withdrawal

308
00:17:13,832 --> 00:17:17,503
will remain on home standby
until the expulsions are finalized.

309
00:17:17,569 --> 00:17:19,104
We'll contact their guardians

310
00:17:19,171 --> 00:17:23,242
and check on the students' well-being.

311
00:17:23,809 --> 00:17:27,479
Please do not interfere
and focus on your normal duties.

312
00:17:39,758 --> 00:17:42,428
INTERCOM - END

313
00:17:45,297 --> 00:17:47,566
It seems Watanuki
asked Kobayakawa's mother

314
00:17:48,300 --> 00:17:51,036
to request that your expulsion
be cancelled.

315
00:17:52,404 --> 00:17:53,572
Hina-chan did it?

316
00:17:54,873 --> 00:17:56,341
What a beautiful friendship.

317
00:18:00,579 --> 00:18:04,516
Your parents have left the matter
entirely up to you.

318
00:18:06,952 --> 00:18:07,986
However…

319
00:18:08,921 --> 00:18:12,191
the school cannot overturn its decision.

320
00:18:13,459 --> 00:18:15,727
Don't get the wrong idea.

321
00:18:15,794 --> 00:18:20,599
Under normal circumstances,
all 11 students could've been expelled.

322
00:18:21,266 --> 00:18:25,304
But the school
doesn't want to abandon its students.

323
00:18:25,971 --> 00:18:28,974
We made a special exception
to help those who show remorse

324
00:18:29,041 --> 00:18:32,678
and want to make amends.

325
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:38,884
We were very careful
in choosing who to expel.

326
00:18:39,918 --> 00:18:41,820
We looked at more than just this incident.

327
00:18:41,887 --> 00:18:47,025
We looked at your usual behavior,
grades, and family situation.

328
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:49,995
If you're not satisfied,

329
00:18:50,629 --> 00:18:54,566
we'll just have to expel all 11 of you.

330
00:19:01,507 --> 00:19:02,574
So…

331
00:19:03,642 --> 00:19:05,043
will you accept the expulsion?

332
00:19:10,883 --> 00:19:11,817
Yes.

333
00:19:12,584 --> 00:19:13,619
I see.

334
00:19:16,255 --> 00:19:19,725
One more thing,

335
00:19:21,193 --> 00:19:23,495
Watanuki and the others
are thoughtful friends.

336
00:19:23,562 --> 00:19:25,998
But they'll only worry about you more.

337
00:19:26,965 --> 00:19:29,535
So if you really care about them,

338
00:19:29,601 --> 00:19:33,906
please stop contacting them.

339
00:19:42,481 --> 00:19:45,083
Life forms that exist on Earth

340
