in the ecosystem…

342
00:19:50,255 --> 00:19:52,257
I don't want to quit school.

343
00:19:52,324 --> 00:19:54,026
Please help me.

344
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:58,830
I'm already working on something,
so wait a little longer.

345
