It's fine.

348
00:20:12,044 --> 00:20:14,346
I've been managing her phone.

349
00:20:15,347 --> 00:20:16,548
I see.

350
00:20:17,416 --> 00:20:20,319
What happened to Iroha's expulsion?

351
