Unfortunately…

352
00:20:24,756 --> 00:20:26,792
She wishes to withdraw.

353
00:20:27,726 --> 00:20:29,728
Iroha? Why?

354
00:20:29,795 --> 00:20:32,598
Apparently, she didn't like school.

355
00:20:33,165 --> 00:20:34,733
-She didn't like it?
-Yes.

356
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:37,102
She was fed up with the people around her.

357
00:20:39,004 --> 00:20:42,140
Surely, you have some idea?

358
00:20:43,242 --> 00:20:47,446
There were incidents
with Iroha, weren't there?

359
