Bet he's up to something again.

361
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:03,028
Huh? Look over there.

362
00:21:12,104 --> 00:21:13,305
Oguchi-sensei.

363
00:21:16,241 --> 00:21:19,311
Moriguchi-sensei wasn't in today.
Do you know what's going on?

364
00:21:19,378 --> 00:21:22,114
What exactly are Moriguchi-sensei
and the vice principal planning?

365
00:21:23,915 --> 00:21:25,651
I honestly don't know.

366
00:21:27,219 --> 00:21:30,055
I'm no longer involved with them.

367
00:21:30,689 --> 00:21:32,891
If you don't like it, that's fine.

368
00:21:32,958 --> 00:21:34,559
If you hate it that much,

369
00:21:35,360 --> 00:21:36,828
then just leave me alone.

370
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:39,031
I think…

371
00:21:40,499 --> 00:21:42,301
I was abandoned.

372
00:21:46,538 --> 00:21:49,007
Why did this happen?

373
00:21:54,346 --> 00:21:58,317
Sorry to call you out so suddenly,
Chairman.

374
00:21:59,584 --> 00:22:01,520
You're here to talk

375
00:22:02,287 --> 00:22:03,322
about Kai, right?

376
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:07,726
The plan to expel 75 students.

377
00:22:08,694 --> 00:22:10,829
Are you really okay with that?

378
00:22:14,099 --> 00:22:15,334
Did something happen to him

379
00:22:16,101 --> 00:22:18,270
during his student years?

380
00:22:20,972 --> 00:22:22,441
What exactly do you know?

381
00:22:22,507 --> 00:22:23,342
Nothing concrete.

382
00:22:24,443 --> 00:22:29,748
As an educator and as a person,

383
00:22:29,815 --> 00:22:32,317
he seems messed up.

384
00:22:32,384 --> 00:22:33,318
So…

385
00:22:34,119 --> 00:22:36,355
I wondered
if something happened in his past.

386
00:22:42,527 --> 00:22:45,330
What about the request
to cancel Naito's expulsion?

387
00:22:45,397 --> 00:22:46,798
Was that resolved?

388
00:22:50,102 --> 00:22:52,971
It's fine. Nothing has changed.

389
00:22:54,239 --> 00:22:57,876
Naito and the other five
will still be expelled.

390
00:22:57,943 --> 00:23:00,178
I'm surprised there wasn't any pushback.

391
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:05,317
The world is full of unfairness,

392
00:23:06,218 --> 00:23:09,521
but how many people actually
stand up to it?

393
00:23:11,690 --> 00:23:12,858
Yes…

394
00:23:12,924 --> 00:23:15,026
Especially in Japan,

395
00:23:15,594 --> 00:23:17,696
people rarely act on their own.

396
00:23:19,431 --> 00:23:21,199
They won't stand up

397
00:23:21,266 --> 00:23:25,203
unless they form a group
and share their thoughts with others.

398
00:23:27,072 --> 00:23:28,840
There are many like that.

399
00:23:31,476 --> 00:23:33,345
If you want to

400
00:23:34,312 --> 00:23:35,614
control people unfairly,

401
00:23:36,415 --> 00:23:38,450
just isolate them.

402
00:23:45,123 --> 00:23:48,493
There were incidents
with Iroha, weren't there?

403
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:51,096
Hina-chan wouldn't do that.

404
