That actually helped me forget
about things for a bit…

427
00:25:44,709 --> 00:25:46,244
Yes!

428
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:58,189
Why are you here?

429
00:25:58,256 --> 00:25:59,691
Why not?

430
00:26:00,458 --> 00:26:02,027
