458
00:27:27,345 --> 00:27:29,381
Is that related somehow?

459
00:27:33,451 --> 00:27:36,054
Before you start worrying
about your students, maybe…

460
00:27:37,022 --> 00:27:40,592
you should worry about yourself.

461
00:27:50,201 --> 00:27:51,369
SEE?

462
00:27:51,436 --> 00:27:54,305
