463
00:27:54,372 --> 00:27:56,708
So you write and post stuff?

464
00:27:56,775 --> 00:27:58,209
That's impressive, Shi-chan.

465
00:27:58,276 --> 00:27:59,778
It's nothing.

466
00:27:59,844 --> 00:28:01,680
I just write about my feelings,
day to day.

467
00:28:01,746 --> 00:28:03,114
She even got so into it,

468
00:28:03,181 --> 00:28:06,651
she made some SEE official stickers.

