483
00:28:57,869 --> 00:29:01,673
My sister is happy with her work.

484
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:04,375
I don't want to bother her.

485
00:29:05,210 --> 00:29:06,945
I see.

486
00:29:07,011 --> 00:29:10,081
But I don't think you should try
to deal with everything on your own.

487
00:29:13,184 --> 00:29:16,154
I'm sick of everything.

488
00:29:16,788 --> 00:29:20,191
But I know I shouldn't run away, right?

489
00:29:23,561 --> 00:29:25,330
That's not true.

490
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:28,366
If it's too painful,
it's okay to run away.

491
00:29:29,134 --> 00:29:30,902
