494
00:29:49,988 --> 00:29:50,822
Thank you.

495
00:29:51,856 --> 00:29:53,391
It's okay to run away.

496
00:29:53,925 --> 00:29:56,494
You have saved me.

497
00:29:56,561 --> 00:29:57,529
THANK YOU…GOODBYE.

