525
00:32:31,716 --> 00:32:33,251
I'm sorry.

526
00:32:33,318 --> 00:32:35,820
I don't even know what I'm saying anymore.

527
00:32:40,224 --> 00:32:41,526
It's okay.

528
00:32:43,127 --> 00:32:45,964
I want to… properly apologize.

529
00:32:47,098 --> 00:32:50,435
But Iroha rejected me.
I don't know what to do.

530
00:32:55,073 --> 00:32:56,074
Sensei…

531
00:32:57,342 --> 00:32:58,876
Please help me.

532
00:33:08,019 --> 00:33:09,587
Urumi-sensei isn't here.

533
00:33:10,188 --> 00:33:12,857
