A teacher, absent without notice?

537
00:33:34,679 --> 00:33:35,980
Tell me.

538
00:33:36,047 --> 00:33:38,549
What did Moriguchi-sensei say?

539
00:33:39,283 --> 00:33:42,820
Urumi-sensei is making
the principal teach her class.

540
00:33:42,887 --> 00:33:44,288
Where is she? What's she doing?

541
00:33:44,355 --> 00:33:45,256
I don't know.

542
00:33:45,323 --> 00:33:48,760
But knowing her, she's
probably doing something for her students.

543
00:33:53,998 --> 00:33:55,166
INCOMING CALL - SHIZUKA URUMI

544
00:33:56,968 --> 00:33:58,703
-Hello?
-Ms. Kyoko.

545
00:33:59,504 --> 00:34:01,639
I'm sorry for skipping school
without permission.

546
00:34:02,673 --> 00:34:03,875
What are you up to?

547
00:34:05,309 --> 00:34:07,445
I'll explain later.

548
00:34:08,546 --> 00:34:12,316
But right now,
there's something I need you to do.

549
00:34:13,751 --> 00:34:14,619
Got it.

550
00:34:19,824 --> 00:34:23,261
Who were you on the phone with, Principal?

551
00:34:24,662 --> 00:34:27,565
Do I need to tell you?

552
00:34:27,632 --> 00:34:28,933
Was it Urumi-sensei?

553
00:34:31,202 --> 00:34:35,072
Whatever she's planning, tell her this.

554
00:34:36,674 --> 00:34:38,810
Don't do anything reckless.

555
00:34:48,686 --> 00:34:50,154
Oh, right.

556
00:34:50,221 --> 00:34:52,590
She asked me something.

557
00:34:52,657 --> 00:34:55,593
She actually had a message for you.

558
00:34:57,328 --> 00:35:00,631
"I'm not going to let things go your way,
dumbass."

559
00:35:02,433 --> 00:35:03,734
That's her message.

560
00:35:10,108 --> 00:35:11,542
What are you doing?

561
00:35:14,378 --> 00:35:16,514
Right now, I'm fired up.

562
00:35:16,581 --> 00:35:18,950
Honestly, I want to protect these girls,
but…

563
00:35:19,016 --> 00:35:22,587
I'm also mad at that guy.
That emotion's even stronger.

564
00:35:23,454 --> 00:35:26,290
Maybe that makes me
a failure as a teacher.

565
00:35:26,357 --> 00:35:27,191
It doesn't matter!

566
00:35:27,925 --> 00:35:30,428
I'm going to shut him down!

567
00:35:31,996 --> 00:35:35,032
KOBAYAKAWA

568
00:35:40,838 --> 00:35:41,772
Sorry, Ms. Kobayakawa.

569
00:35:42,673 --> 00:35:44,008
We dropped by unannounced.

570
00:35:45,243 --> 00:35:46,110
Why are you here?

571
00:35:46,177 --> 00:35:48,779
We need to see your mom.

572
00:35:48,846 --> 00:35:51,983
And ask her to request the school
to cancel Iroha's expulsion!

573
00:35:56,354 --> 00:35:57,655
You should go home for today.

574
00:35:58,222 --> 00:35:59,824
-Why?
-Mai?

575
00:36:02,493 --> 00:36:03,995
Oh… do we have guests?

576
00:36:05,563 --> 00:36:07,098
And you are?

577
00:36:07,165 --> 00:36:09,467
I'm Shizuka Urumi, Mai's homeroom teacher.

578
00:36:10,434 --> 00:36:11,536
Her teacher?

579
00:36:13,171 --> 00:36:14,438
I knew you'd show up.

580
00:36:24,015 --> 00:36:26,350
"I'm not going to let things go your way."

581
00:36:27,351 --> 00:36:29,520
You sent that childish message.

582
00:36:32,223 --> 00:36:34,792
You didn't think I'd be here, did you?

583
00:36:38,196 --> 00:36:39,397
I figured you'd show up.

584
00:36:41,098 --> 00:36:43,301
You, with your clingy personality,

585
00:36:43,367 --> 00:36:46,337
are the type who always interferes.

586
00:36:47,171 --> 00:36:49,073
So I sent that message on purpose.

587
00:36:51,142 --> 00:36:52,343
Still acting tough, huh?

588
00:36:52,410 --> 00:36:54,145
I'm not acting.

589
00:36:55,413 --> 00:36:57,215
Even if I convinced Mai's mom,

590
00:36:57,281 --> 00:37:00,284
you'd just scheme behind the scenes again.

591
00:37:01,419 --> 00:37:04,155
That's why I decided
to take one you two altogether.

592
00:37:07,458 --> 00:37:08,826
SCRIPT

593
00:37:10,628 --> 00:37:12,196
Moriguchi-sensei,

594
00:37:13,564 --> 00:37:14,865
in this incident,

595
00:37:15,766 --> 00:37:18,736
students who committed the same offense
were treated differently.

596
00:37:18,803 --> 00:37:21,872
Some were expelled, others suspended.

597
00:37:21,939 --> 00:37:23,941
Can you give a clear explanation?

598
00:37:25,576 --> 00:37:29,313
.It was based on
whether they showed remorse,

599
00:37:30,047 --> 00:37:33,150
as well as an overall assessment
of their daily conduct.

600
00:37:33,217 --> 00:37:34,952
And what's your standard

601
00:37:35,019 --> 00:37:37,588
for judging whether someone's remorseful?

602
00:37:37,655 --> 00:37:40,825
And what exactly do you mean
by "daily conduct"?

603
00:37:40,891 --> 00:37:42,960
I don't find your explanation
convincing at all.

604
00:37:43,728 --> 00:37:44,962
Also you…

605
00:37:45,029 --> 00:37:48,032
You panicked and lied, didn't you?

606
00:37:49,634 --> 00:37:51,969
It happens when you're young.

607
00:37:52,036 --> 00:37:53,971
Lying…

608
00:37:54,038 --> 00:37:57,408
just to save yourself
is a selfish mindset.

609
00:37:58,809 --> 00:38:02,179
We can't expect
someone like that to repent and improve.

610
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:05,316
You change your definition of "a lie"
for each student.

611
00:38:06,217 --> 00:38:08,686
How you respond differs
based on who the student is.

612
00:38:09,253 --> 00:38:12,623
That's the worst thing a teacher can do.

613
00:38:15,393 --> 00:38:16,427
Ms. Kobayakawa,

614
00:38:17,795 --> 00:38:20,431
as PTA President, what do you think?

615
00:38:22,500 --> 00:38:24,201
Or did you already know,

616
00:38:24,268 --> 00:38:27,038
but decided it didn't matter
as long as your daughter was safe?

617
00:38:27,104 --> 00:38:29,707
You didn't come to that conclusion,
did you?

618
00:38:29,774 --> 00:38:31,942
Mom… Is that true?

619
00:38:32,810 --> 00:38:34,445
Of course not!

620
00:38:36,614 --> 00:38:38,382
That's a relief.

621
00:38:40,117 --> 00:38:42,987
As the PTA President,

622
00:38:43,054 --> 00:38:45,690
there's no way someone like you
would play favorites, right?

623
00:38:51,162 --> 00:38:52,263
Now then,

624
00:38:53,197 --> 00:38:56,801
why would Moriguchi-sensei
do such a thing?

625
00:39:00,271 --> 00:39:01,939
That doesn't matter right now.

626
00:39:03,541 --> 00:39:06,043
What's important today

627
00:39:06,110 --> 00:39:08,112
is getting the school to cancel

628
00:39:08,179 --> 00:39:10,581
its recommendation for Naito

629
00:39:13,417 --> 00:39:15,820
and the other five students to quit.

630
00:39:18,189 --> 00:39:19,590
Let me be blunt.

631
00:39:19,657 --> 00:39:23,294
If this goes to court,
the school will almost certainly lose.

632
00:39:26,263 --> 00:39:29,367
They all did the same thing,
yet the punishments vary.

633
00:39:29,433 --> 00:39:30,668
Any judge would rule that

634
00:39:31,302 --> 00:39:35,673
the recommendation for them to quit
lacks legitimacy and is illegal.

635
00:39:37,508 --> 00:39:39,844
You never should've
recommended expulsion in the first--

636
00:39:51,922 --> 00:39:53,791
Sorry to say,

637
00:39:53,858 --> 00:39:56,427
but the school's decision
won't be overturned.

638
00:39:58,996 --> 00:40:00,831
If you want to file a lawsuit, go ahead.

639
00:40:01,399 --> 00:40:03,467
But where will you get the money
to hire a lawyer?

640
00:40:03,534 --> 00:40:05,903
Do you know how long a lawsuit takes?

641
00:40:08,139 --> 00:40:10,608
It's expensive and a hassle.

642
00:40:10,674 --> 00:40:13,310
It would be better to

643
00:40:13,377 --> 00:40:16,313
just transfer their kid to a new school.

644
00:40:16,380 --> 00:40:18,983
There are many parents like that.

645
00:40:20,684 --> 00:40:21,619
Right…

646
00:40:22,520 --> 00:40:23,888
Naito?

647
00:40:28,659 --> 00:40:29,693
I see.

648
00:40:32,530 --> 00:40:34,732
If Naito won't act herself,

649
00:40:35,533 --> 00:40:37,635
then there's nothing we can do.

650
00:40:42,339 --> 00:40:44,875
Then why don't you quit along with Naito?

651
00:40:45,643 --> 00:40:47,011
What are you saying?

652
00:40:47,077 --> 00:40:50,681
Your friend's getting expelled.
But you aren't. Does that make it okay?

653
00:40:51,549 --> 00:40:53,050
Are you really fine with that?

654
00:40:54,952 --> 00:40:58,522
You broke the rules by smoking.

655
00:40:58,589 --> 00:41:01,425
You must reflect on that, of course.

656
00:41:02,893 --> 00:41:06,163
But can you really say you've made amends
if you abandon your friend?

657
00:41:07,097 --> 00:41:10,234
Even if guilt fades with time,

658
00:41:10,868 --> 00:41:13,737
the fact you betrayed someone
will stay with you forever.

659
00:41:13,804 --> 00:41:16,407
It will come back to you.

660
00:41:17,107 --> 00:41:18,876
-So--
-Enough already!

661
00:41:18,943 --> 00:41:21,178
-How long are you going to--
-I'll…

662
00:41:22,346 --> 00:41:23,581
I'll quit, too!

663
00:41:27,651 --> 00:41:29,553
It's not right
that only Iroha gets expelled

664
00:41:30,387 --> 00:41:32,223
while the rest of us are spared.

665
00:41:34,692 --> 00:41:39,063
If Iroha and Hina are leaving,
then so am I.

666
00:41:39,129 --> 00:41:40,531
Mai, what are you saying?

667
00:41:40,598 --> 00:41:42,533
I would never allow that!

668
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:46,504
You… only cared about me!

669
00:41:46,570 --> 00:41:48,372
Do you want me to be such a coward?

670
00:41:49,507 --> 00:41:50,608
No…

671
00:41:53,444 --> 00:41:54,645
Ms. Kobayakawa,

672
00:41:57,281 --> 00:42:00,117
If this continues,
everyone will end up expelled.

673
00:42:09,393 --> 00:42:10,794
Moriguchi-sensei,

674
00:42:14,265 --> 00:42:15,966
I think

675
00:42:16,033 --> 00:42:20,004
expelling six students
over this is a bit too much.

676
00:42:21,372 --> 00:42:22,840
Please, could you give everyone

677
00:42:23,541 --> 00:42:25,943
the same disciplinary suspension instead?

678
00:42:30,414 --> 00:42:34,084
As PTA President, I'm asking you a favor.

679
00:42:34,785 --> 00:42:36,253
You understand, don't you?

680
00:42:46,463 --> 00:42:49,366
Dammit!

681
00:42:49,934 --> 00:42:53,103
Dammit!

682
00:42:56,173 --> 00:42:57,074
Thanks.

683
00:42:59,610 --> 00:43:02,913
When you said
you'd quit with me, honestly,

684
00:43:02,980 --> 00:43:04,014
I was really happy.

685
00:43:04,081 --> 00:43:05,749
I wanted to say,

686
00:43:06,383 --> 00:43:08,085
"Of course I would," but…

687
00:43:08,152 --> 00:43:10,387
the truth is, Shizuka-sensei told me
to do it.

688
00:43:11,155 --> 00:43:12,256
What?

689
00:43:13,757 --> 00:43:18,495
When I ask "Why don't you
quit with Naito," go along with it.

690
00:43:21,231 --> 00:43:22,533
I just passed that message

691
00:43:22,600 --> 00:43:24,134
along to Mai.

692
00:43:26,570 --> 00:43:28,906
But I'm really glad we did it.

693
00:43:31,675 --> 00:43:32,710
I'm glad.

694
00:43:38,515 --> 00:43:39,917
Okay, let's head back.

695
00:43:41,719 --> 00:43:42,753
Sensei.

696
00:43:44,021 --> 00:43:44,855
Thank you.

697
00:43:45,823 --> 00:43:46,657
Thank you.

698
00:43:47,958 --> 00:43:49,560
No need to thank me.

699
00:43:49,627 --> 00:43:51,528
Just carry out your suspension properly.

700
00:43:57,534 --> 00:43:58,769
Are you crying?

701
00:43:58,836 --> 00:44:01,739
-You're crying!
-I'm not!

702
00:44:01,805 --> 00:44:04,675
SHIZUKA URUMI IS A MURDERER.

703
00:44:07,244 --> 00:44:08,812
The one who posted this

704
00:44:10,614 --> 00:44:12,116
was Aika-sensei, right?

705
00:44:16,687 --> 00:44:17,755
Yes.

706
00:44:20,057 --> 00:44:21,659
She doesn't remember.

707
00:44:23,394 --> 00:44:24,728
Even after meeting me.

708
00:44:42,980 --> 00:44:45,349
You murdered my little sister.

709
00:44:50,020 --> 00:44:51,855
Can you all knock it off already?

710
00:44:51,922 --> 00:44:53,323
A HOSTAGE SITUATION
AT A SCHOOL ON SUNDAY?

711
00:44:53,390 --> 00:44:54,525
Coward!
